# Hugo and Jekyll Supported Code Block Languages

The full language identifier list below is part of Cursor rules.

# Supported code block languages

This is the full list of language identifiers (aliases included) for Hugo syntax highlighting (Chroma), based on Hugo docs. It can be use for Jekyll also.

Source: https://gohugo.io/content-management/syntax-highlighting/#languages

Use one of these identifiers as `LANG` in fenced code blocks.

